description: Gia is in a very precarious situation. Master has tied her very securely to his favorite chair, her legs are pulled apart to expose her most venerable area. He quickly gags her in anticipation of her protests. Gia takes a deep breath, her eyes open wide as she sees Master walk towards her. She cringes as she thinks of the punishment for complaining to much and knows she will never be able to remain silent, regardless of the consequences.
title: Close Encounters
